# Cloudflare static-asset response headers (Workers/Pages `_headers` format).
# Our deploy is pure-static (no Worker script), so these apply to every asset.

# The generated llms*.txt files are plain-text mirrors of the docs for AI/coding
# agents (Cursor, Cline, etc.). Keep them fetchable by crawlers, but OUT of
# Google's web index — they are not pages meant to rank, and indexing them would
# just create thin/duplicate results. (Verified 2026: llms.txt is not an SEO/GEO
# citation lever — it exists only for the IDE-agent audience.)
/llms.txt
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex
/llms-full.txt
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex
/llms-small.txt
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex
